<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body, .container {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .center-text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px; /* Adjust margin top as needed */
        }
        .about-text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px; /* Adjust margin top as needed */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Adjust margin bottom as needed */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Home</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/producttab">Products</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Services</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/profile">Profile</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1>Welcome to NicPetBuddies !</h1>
        <hr style="border-top: 1px solid #110f0f; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-text">
                <p>At NicPetBuddies, we're dedicated to becoming your ultimate destination for all things pet-related. While we've just launched, our commitment to enhancing your pet care experience is unwavering. Currently, our platform offers a selection of essential pet products, and we're excited to announce that more features and services are on their way.</p>
    
                <p>Thank you for supporting us on this journey to provide exceptional care and products for your beloved pets. Stay tuned as we grow and expand to meet all your pet care needs!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Bootstrap Carousel -->
        <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide mt-4" data-bs-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="images/home2.png" class="d-block w-100">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5>Love animals?</h5>
                        <p>Sign up to be a petsitter now!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="images/home3.png" class="d-block w-100">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5> Nothing to do this weekend ?</h5>
                        <p> Hurry book your slots to petsit this weekend!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="images/home4.png" class="d-block w-100">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <h5> Animal supplies lying around the house? </h5>
                        <p> Sell them here !</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleControls" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Bootstrap JS bundle (required) -->

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.12.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
